data.title: Human Rights Campaign
data.meta_description: The Human Rights Campaign envisions a world where every member of the LGBTQ+ family has the freedom to live their truth without fear, and with equality under the law. We empower our 3 million members and supporters to mobilize against attacks on the most marginalized people in our community.
data.text:
Vice President Harris and Governor Walz have shown up for the LGBTQ+ community time and time again. Now, it’s our turn to show up for them.

Join the Human Rights Campaign in organizing and securing big wins in November and beyond—take action and get involved!

Equality Magazine: Spring 2024

We Show Up

This November, we show up to defend our democracy for future generations. We show up to reject extreme government control over our lives, personal decisions and how we raise families. we show up to protect best practice healthcare for kids. We show up to protect our rights to love who we love and live our most authentic lives unapologetically. We show up until every last one of us is fully free and liberated – without exception and with no one left behind.
